om the pre-payment to the pay-out process. PayMoney is a much simpler & convenient way to send money online rather than going to bank or other ways. Just follow the PayMoney documentation to get started.', 3, '2020-04-13 14:51:44', '2021-09-10', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 4, 2, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 12.00000000, NULL, 0, 0),(135, 'New feature - selection of fiat currency wallets during user registration', 'A point of sale inventory management system allows a business owner to have more than one business location and adequately keep track of inventory at each without being present — no more worries about employee theft or pricing inconsistency between one location and another.', 1, '2020-04-13 14:54:48', '2021-09-10', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 4, 1, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),(136, 'Property Inspection Request while users is submitting properties', 'Vacation Rental Marketplace by techvillage1 on CodeCanyon. Support/Help are provided by Support Ticket. Please send us e-mail for further info.', 1, '2020-04-13 14:58:11', '2021-09-10', '2021-09-17', NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 3, 1, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),(137, 'Add host messages option by admin and update some task in vrent admin panel', 'vRent is an online vacation rental booking website designed particularly for holiday rentals all over the world. vRent is exclusively designed to satisfy the needs of the landlords who want to seriously make money by listing vacation rentals from all around the globe. vRent allows you to create your own vacation rental platform to help guests to find space for a cost.', 1, '2020-04-13 15:01:11', '2021-09-10', '2021-09-17', NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 4, 2, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 5.00000000, NULL, 0, 0);
